# Peer-build ignore (BuildKit uses <dockerfile>.dockerignore over the repo root
# one). Unlike the root .dockerignore, we KEEP web/dist — revenant-control
# embeds it at compile time (rust-embed), so excluding it breaks the build.
.git
target
**/target
**/node_modules
**/*.rs.bk
**/.DS_Store
**/secrets.env
demos/horde/*.log
